18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=db34b534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=48f01a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">喂<br />\n唔夠膽應呀？<br />\n唔好轉移視線啦</span>"},{"pid":"71b93233b22e280f8b3a3e15c982c6a9d5e3aa5c","tid":923074,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e9608c59a30ccb786cfca974a0364fca728e0b52","tid":923074,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6388decc239e39ab3f77c34d63fc99d164189ac9","tid":923074,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4b0eda2e3e7c1c69528614a0d92632f81568f5c","tid":923074,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"只要保皇狗一直控制議會 標準工時永都唔會有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bPyAvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bPyAvS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家睇下我專登講保皇狗反對標準工時<br />\n關愛座hunter入去落係屌保皇狗<br />\n而係貼保皇狗以外政黨去轉載視<br />\n關愛座huntet你不如講下點解咁做？</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"呀五毛#38523不如答吓<br />\n關鍵一席就缺席投票係咩玩法?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"大陸間碟<br />\n我話保皇狗反對標準工時你問我關鍵一席係咩玩法？<br />\n先唔講依加鍵一席已經係保皇狗手<br />\n你樣唔樣衰d<br />\n你呢鋪真係現晒形<br />\n咁又係<br />\n一個為錢去大陸做野既人<br />\n有咩做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸間碟<br />\n又係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">哦<br />\n即係泛民將關鍵一席送咗畀親中派啦<br />\n關我咩事?</span>"},{"pid":"26a44bde5cc188689bff9243e914870e430a738f","tid":923074,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f000484bfed3b4ec897803cdade80431ab8af16","tid":923074,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"82a8f5eab36bcb95354d0a482c9e41592cae1289","tid":923074,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"eb461f86a6e16f12565982641840ce3fa4be8198","tid":923074,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">青衣單車禍一出<br />\n原來司機工時咁長<br />\n一見我開post保皇狗反對標準工時<br />\n你唔單止入去用其他黨轉載視線對保皇狗隻字不提<br />\n依加又即刻開post？<br />\n大家都睇得出你隻大陸間碟係保皇狗打手</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">噉有冇做過先?改名五毛五毛狙擊手#38523?<br />\n</span><br />\n重有大把缺席投票紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nKAS2G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nKAS2G.jpg&h=a95583d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ba1afa09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"htt